Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.05,0:22:38.33,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Eu só quero ficar assim
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:42.64,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Não me force assim...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.64,0:22:45.81,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Porém...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.81,0:22:54.93,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Era para ser uma fortaleza que ninguém iria penetrar
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:23:07.96,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Deveria ser impenetrável, mas por quê?
